# Session 2 (Andrea Jabbour)

## Implemented Features
- Created and configured the ASP.NET Core Web API project.
- Implemented the `Product` and `Supplier` domain models.
- Created DTOs for product and supplier requests.
- Added in-memory data stores for products and suppliers.
- Implemented product management endpoints.
- Implemented supplier management endpoints.
- Implemented product-supplier assignment.
- Added product image upload with validation.
- Implemented soft delete and restore functionality.
- Added warehouse utility endpoints for products and suppliers.
- Configured and tested the API using Swagger.

## Run Instructions

1. Clone the repository.
2. Open the solution in Rider.
3. Restore the NuGet packages.
4. Build and run the project.
5. Open Swagger to test the API (http://localhost:5000/swagger/index.html)

